    {
      "id": "ef4526420efdef0cbc2689c9de47571b6abfb66b",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 626,
        "name": "Quentin Bouget",
        "email": "quentin.bouget@cea.fr",
        "username": "bougetq"
      },
      "date": "2017-06-30 12:16:25.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1\n\nThis patch set is based on Andreas' suggestion that \"scan policies\" could be defined in separate and loadable modules.\n\nThere are several issues I am aware of: there is a memory leak (I don't know where), the packaging is wrong (you cannot run \"make\" twice in a row), I ended up needing to export more functions from the mdt module than I hoped for.\n\nI am only pushing this patch set so that we can work with a common code base.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "db9476f97c7b96feb72d1f2af3d75f61c86e7dfc",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2017-07-04 21:48:35.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(8 comments)",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "25f9fd648c894bae74fae174da97fcbdf1b8ab4e",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2017-07-04 21:50:07.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nPlease also note that if having a separately-loadable coordinator module is too complex, that is not a requirement for your patch to land.  Rather, it was a suggestion on how the code might be more flexible for future development, but possibly the code is too tightly coupled to make this practical right now.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "b6af2d27b9ab97fd0f31007d4ba689f3f5afa9a5",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 626,
        "name": "Quentin Bouget",
        "email": "quentin.bouget@cea.fr",
        "username": "bougetq"
      },
      "date": "2017-07-07 11:01:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> Please also note that if having a separately-loadable coordinator module is too complex, that is not a requirement for your patch to land.\n\nYes, I know that this is too much to land in 2.10.X. But the idea is really interesting and I am keeping it for later. I will roll back to the previous patch set soon.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
